&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a paediatric nurse to join our Outpatient team. If you are interested in developing your career in a busy clinic environment we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly, supportive team that is passionate about delivering first class care to the families and patients who access our service, whilst working closely with other members of the multi-disciplinary team. We provide holistic family centred care that we are proud of and that we know makes a difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you access and support to undertake additional training, regular team days and clinical supervision. There is also the opportunity to work on other areas within our Children&#39;s Unit which includes Holly Ward, Daycase and our assessment unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a flexible individual to work part time hours (22.5hrs) to join our team. Our current working hours within outpatients are Monday - Friday 9 - 5.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/p&gt;
